.B \-noshiftbracket
Emulate [, \(rs, ], \(ha and _ as unshifted keys, and {, |, }, and \(ti as
shifted.
This is the default in Model I and III modes, and it works well with many TRS-80
keyboard drivers.
With some keyboard drivers these keys do not work at all, however.
