.I disk1-0
and
.IR disk1-2 ,
and single-steps
.IR disk1-1 .
.TP
.B \-sizemap \fIs0\
\fR[\fB,\fIz1\
\fR[\fB,\fIz2\
\fR[\fB,\fIz3\
\fR[\fB,\fIz4\
\fR[\fB,\fIz5\
\fR[\fB,\fIz6\
\fR[\fB,\fIz7\
\fR]]]]]]]
Selectively set whether drives are emulated as
.5-1/4
-inch or 8-inch; see
